      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in impeccable, mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the factory. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine interior upholstery, has been meticulously preserved. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained to the highest standards. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality example that looks and drives like new.",
      "price": 49000.0,
